    public static class CayleyCoverageRadius.RadiusMap
extends MathMap<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Float>
    A map from trace length ℓ to a rational number between 0 and 1. This number indicates how much coverage is achieved for equivalence classes reachable by a trace of length ℓ or less.
